item.title: About me
item.description: I’m an electronic engineer who studied at the University of Seville and have been working in the aerospace industry for close to 10 years now.

item.title: Into the future...
item.description: AI will likely continue to progress at an unprecedented rate, with the emergence of new breakthroughs and applications. Ethical considerations must be prioritized in AI development.
